Package: droughtmonitor
Title: An API Wrapper for U.S. Drought Monitor
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Dylan", "Turner", , "dylan.turner3@outlook.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = 0000-0002-0915-7384))
Description: `droughtmonitor` is a simple API wrapper for the U.S. Drought Monitor API. The package provides a set of functions for easily locating and obtaining data related to present and historical drought conditions in the United States.
